<br>
 Found an unsolved, undocumented wiz quest from the library in Erudin. I received the quest only after reaching 20th from Weltria Ostriss in the city library. Takes you deep into the Warrens, and indeed requires a group. Im 24th now and have completed HALF the initial requirements, I suspect I'll be 30th upon completion! /laugh...<br>
 <br>
