In guk, if you have help getting the rod, see if they can help getting your Rune of Scale (Runescale Cloak), and the Glowing Mask (Acumen Mask).<br>
In Lake Rathe, check the skely tower for a camp. The Rod of Bone (Staff of Temp.Flux) drops here (wiz only!), and most let you grab it as your going by...<br>
<br>
 Check the quests for better details, except the Warrens quest. Been diggin deep and finding nothing on this AT ALL...<br>
<br>
 Good huntin! Yaht<br>
